    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I am so excited to show you this car. It is absolutely gorgeous and in truly incredible shape\u2014it basically feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
