      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable 2011 BMW M3 Coupe (E92), a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This specimen features the legendary S65 4.0L V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and an M-Variable differential lock for optimal lateral dynamics. Meticulously maintained, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed preventatively. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory-fresh matte finish. This is a collector-grade example with zero deferred maintenance, offering a visceral analog driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
