    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in absolute showroom condition. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is entirely free of swirls, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive paper trail included. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched trunk, every detail reflects a life of fastidious care. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
